145
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:36,790
♪Jika aku tak berjalan menghampiri♪

146
00:13:37,030 --> 00:13:41,320
♪Apakah kau hanya bisa mondar-mandir?♪

147
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:48,760
♪Suara daun yang tertiup angin
Tak berani terlalu keras♪

148
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:53,790
♪Suara jantung yang berdebar kencang
