212
00:17:40,640 --> 00:17:41,700
Kau akan ke dunia manusia.

213
00:17:41,700 --> 00:17:42,680
(Paviliun Luofeng)

214
00:17:42,680 --> 00:17:44,280
Kau hanya perlu melewati
Jembatan Luofeng ini.

215
00:17:44,830 --> 00:17:47,470
♪Cahaya bulan di dalam hati
